  "detailed_description": "The Faceless Man is a first-person horror game inspired by an old creepypasta about a Tall Thin Man. Brace yourself to confront one of the victims of the ancient legend known as The Faceless Man, whose intentions remain shrouded in mystery.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931530/extras/2506227d961ce310079cce71681c20f6.poster.avif?t=1716583053\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931530/extras/2506227d961ce310079cce71681c20f6.webm?t=1716583053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931530/extras/2506227d961ce310079cce71681c20f6.mp4?t=1716583053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Powered by the powerful Unreal Engine 5, The Faceless Man offers modern mechanics and stunning graphics without requiring high-end machines to run.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931530/extras/d43b75453eb9911bf1ce309a51fda2c8.poster.avif?t=1716583053\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931530/extras/d43b75453eb9911bf1ce309a51fda2c8.webm?t=1716583053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931530/extras/d43b75453eb9911bf1ce309a51fda2c8.mp4?t=1716583053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>GAME HIGHLIGHTS:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Face the Unknown:</strong> Enter the dark and unsettling world of the Faceless Man, where the mystery is as immersive as the terror.<br></li><li><strong>Cutting-Edge Graphics:</strong> Impressive visuals powered by Unreal Engine 5, ensuring a visually striking and realistic atmosphere.<br></li><li><strong>Innovative Mechanics:</strong> Experience modern and engaging gameplay, with mechanics that maintain tension from start to finish.<br></li><li><strong>Gamepad Compatibility: </strong>Immerse yourself in the terrifying experience with native gamepad support, providing precise and intuitive control.<br></li><li><strong>Language Diversity:</strong> Enjoy full immersion in different languages, with support for English, Brazilian Portuguese, Spanish, Simplified Chinese, French, German, Italian, Japanese, and Russian.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931530/extras/59fa15454942b5faca631cfa598d530f.poster.avif?t=1716583053\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931530/extras/59fa15454942b5faca631cfa598d530f.webm?t=1716583053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931530/extras/59fa15454942b5faca631cfa598d530f.mp4?t=1716583053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "The Faceless Man is a first-person horror game inspired by an old creepypasta about a Tall Thin Man. Brace yourself to confront one of the victims of the ancient legend known as The Faceless Man, whose intentions remain shrouded in mystery.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931530/extras/2506227d961ce310079cce71681c20f6.poster.avif?t=1716583053\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931530/extras/2506227d961ce310079cce71681c20f6.webm?t=1716583053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931530/extras/2506227d961ce310079cce71681c20f6.mp4?t=1716583053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Powered by the powerful Unreal Engine 5, The Faceless Man offers modern mechanics and stunning graphics without requiring high-end machines to run.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931530/extras/d43b75453eb9911bf1ce309a51fda2c8.poster.avif?t=1716583053\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931530/extras/d43b75453eb9911bf1ce309a51fda2c8.webm?t=1716583053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931530/extras/d43b75453eb9911bf1ce309a51fda2c8.mp4?t=1716583053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>GAME HIGHLIGHTS:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Face the Unknown:</strong> Enter the dark and unsettling world of the Faceless Man, where the mystery is as immersive as the terror.<br></li><li><strong>Cutting-Edge Graphics:</strong> Impressive visuals powered by Unreal Engine 5, ensuring a visually striking and realistic atmosphere.<br></li><li><strong>Innovative Mechanics:</strong> Experience modern and engaging gameplay, with mechanics that maintain tension from start to finish.<br></li><li><strong>Gamepad Compatibility: </strong>Immerse yourself in the terrifying experience with native gamepad support, providing precise and intuitive control.<br></li><li><strong>Language Diversity:</strong> Enjoy full immersion in different languages, with support for English, Brazilian Portuguese, Spanish, Simplified Chinese, French, German, Italian, Japanese, and Russian.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931530/extras/59fa15454942b5faca631cfa598d530f.poster.avif?t=1716583053\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931530/extras/59fa15454942b5faca631cfa598d530f.webm?t=1716583053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931530/extras/59fa15454942b5faca631cfa598d530f.mp4?t=1716583053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
